---

## Installation

```
npm i
```

## Running in dev mode

```
npm start <day>
```

Example:

```
npm start 1
```

## Work Specific Setup

Workaround for proxy (add to .env file): `NODE_TLS_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED=0`

Use correct node version (need nvm installed): `nvm use`
